NV/LIB/STR

result = str_create_descriptors(n, end_keywords, crd=crd, bd=bd, sld=sld, gbd=gbd, sd=sd, abbrev=abbrev, user=user, name=name, tasks=tasks, udata=udata, uname=uname, assoc_xd=assoc_xd, fn_body_to_inertial=fn_body_to_inertial, fn_inertial_to_body=fn_inertial_to_body, ib_data_=ib_data_, time=time, orient=orient, avel=avel, pos=pos, vel=vel, opaque=opaque, libv=libv, __lib=__lib, dlibdt=dlibdt, array=array, opacity=opacity, mass=mass, GM=GM, refl_fn=refl_fn, refl_parm=refl_parm, phase_fn=phase_fn, phase_parm=phase_parm, albedo=albedo, type=type, radii=radii, lora=lora, lref=lref, rref=rref, J=J, lum=lum, sp=sp)

Init method for the STAR class.

Return value

An array (n) of star descriptors. STATUS: Completed.

Parameters

n in

Number of star descriptors.

end_keywords

Keywords

crd in

Core descriptor(s) to pass to cor_create_descriptors.

bd in

Body descriptor(s) to pass to bod_create_descriptors.

sld in

Solid descriptor(s) to pass to sld_create_descriptors.

gbd in

Globe descriptor(s) to pass to glb_create_descriptors.

sd in

Star descriptor(s) to initialize, instead of creating new ones.
